reviewText: WHAT A RIP OFF !!!!  all it is a 20 MINUTE debate between 2 priests , and a 1 minute blurb of an "actual" exorcism going on .....(which was poor) . I've NEVER been so disappointed in a dvd - EVER.

A very interesting interview with Fr James Le Bar, noted exorcist and author. A very eloquent and clearly experienced man in the field defending the decision to televise the exorcism. Really worth watching just for that.
